title: Looking for supp(Gold 5+) for all Gold Team Flex
body:
Hey,

Team looking for gold 5+ support to play ranked flex q seriously on a daily basis. Nothing too serious but with the intention of climbing. Team consists of all gold5+ players, spiking with plat 5 adc. 

Use discord to communicate and joke, play 1-2 games a day, can rotate the positions every now and then if you dont want to be supp permanently. 

Message me at Kássadin 

See you on the rift
